1 (2) Subdivision (d)(1) of this section does not prohibit the
2 adoption of a local ordinance or regulation that regulates certain specifics
3 impacting vegetable gardens, including without limitation the use of water
4 during drought conditions, fertilizer use, control of invasive species and
5 weeds, and reasonable size and location specifics related to permissible
6 vegetable garden locations including without limitation side yards or
7 backyards.
